     +-----------------------+   +-----------+
     |    Web Layer          |   |           |
     |   (controllers) (3)   |   |    DTO(1) |
     +-----------------------+   |           |
     +-----------------------+   |           |
     |    Service Layer(2)   |   +-----------+
     |                       |   +-----------+
     +-----------------------+   |  Domain   |
     +-----------------------+   |  Model    |
     |    Repository Layer   |   | (Entity)  |
     |                       |   |  Posts    |
     +-----------------------+   +-----------+

