조회
+-----------------------------+
|  Java Application           |
|                             |
|     +------------------+    |
|     | JPA              |    |
|     | +--------------+ |    |            +---------+
|     | |  JDBC        + +----+---SQL--->  |   DB    |
|     | |  API         + +<---+---Ret----  |         |
|     | +--------------+ |    |            +---------+
|     +------------------+    |
+-----------------------------+

저장
+---------------------------------------------+
|                                             |
|   +-----------+              +------------+ |
|   |           |   (Entity)   | JPA        | |
|   |   Member  | --Persist -->|  +-------+ | |
|   |   DAO     |              |  | JDBC  | + +---(insert SQL) ---> DB
|   |           |              |  +-------+ | |
|   +-----------+              +------------+ |
|                                             |
+---------------------------------------------+


저장
+---------------------------------------------+
|                                             |
|   +-----------+              +------------+ |
|   |           |              | JPA        | |
|   |   Member  |--find(id)--->|  +-------+ | |                     +------+
|   |   DAO     |              |  | JDBC  | + +---(insert SQL) ---> |  DB  |
|   |           |    (entity)  |  | API   | | |<------ Ret -------- |      |
|   |           |<-- (object) -|  +-------+ | |                     +------+
|   +-----------+              +------------+ |
|                                             |
+---------------------------------------------+